Decreased AC by 2 (Lvl 1) to 18 (Lvl 59)<br>
Decreased STR by 11 (Lvl 1) to 69 (Lvl 59)<br>
The effect lasts for 84 seconds.  <br>
<br>
Tier IV Increased Attack speed by 25%<br>
Decreased AC by 2 (Lvl 1) to 20 (Lvl 60)<br>
Decreased STR by 11 (Lvl 1) to 70 (Lvl 60)<br>
The effect lasts for 96 seconds.  <br>
